topology - package topology
 
Topology1D - Class in topology
An object that specifies how a CellArray1D should retrieve neighborhoods.
Topology1D(Topology1D.Base, int, Topology1D.Space) - Constructor for class topology.Topology1D
Creates a Topology1D object that specifies how a CellArray1D should retrieve neighborhoods.
Topology1D.Base - Enum in topology
An enumeration of the supported neighborhood geometries: radial, left, right, Each item has a field containing the appropriate method name in CellArray1D so that a Topology1D object can specify which method the target CellArray1D should use for neighborhood lookup.
Topology1D.Circle - Class in topology
The Standard topology inner class for subsets of R^1 where all boundary points are identified with themselves.
Topology1D.Circle() - Constructor for class topology.Topology1D.Circle
 
Topology1D.Space - Enum in topology
An enumeration of the supported identity spaces: Standard, Circle Each item has a field containing the name of the inner class in Topology1D which contains the appropriate identity functions for that identity space.
Topology1D.Standard - Class in topology
The Standard topology inner class for subsets of R^2 where all boundary points are identified with themselves.
Topology1D.Standard() - Constructor for class topology.Topology1D.Standard
 
Topology2D - Class in topology
An object that specifies how a CellArray2D should retrieve neighborhoods.
Topology2D(Topology2D.Base, int, Topology2D.Space) - Constructor for class topology.Topology2D
Creates a Topology2D object that specifies how a CellArray2D should retrieve neighborhoods.
Topology2D.Base - Enum in topology
An enumeration of the supported neighborhood geometries: Moore, Von Neumann, Left Corners, Right Corners, Horizontal, Vertical, Left Diagonal, Right Diagonal.
Topology2D.Cylinder - Class in topology
A topology inner class for subsets of R^2 that directly identifies the left and right boundaries to each other and all points on the top and bottom boundaries are identified with themselves.
Topology2D.Cylinder() - Constructor for class topology.Topology2D.Cylinder
 
Topology2D.Klein - Class in topology
A topology inner class for subsets of R^2 that identifies the left and right hand boundaries to each other with a 180 degree twist and directly identifies the top and bottom boundaries to each other.
Topology2D.Klein() - Constructor for class topology.Topology2D.Klein
 
Topology2D.Moebius - Class in topology
A topology inner class for subsets of R^2 that identifies the left and right hand boundaries to each other with a 180 degree twist and all points on the top and bottom boundaries are identified with themselves.
Topology2D.Moebius() - Constructor for class topology.Topology2D.Moebius
 
Topology2D.Space - Enum in topology
An enumeration of the supported identity spaces: Standard, Cylinder, Moebius Band.
Topology2D.Standard - Class in topology
The Standard topology inner class for subsets of R^2 where all boundary points are identified with themselves.
Topology2D.Standard() - Constructor for class topology.Topology2D.Standard
 
Topology2D.Torus - Class in topology
A topology inner class for subsets of R^2 that directly identifies the left and right boundaries to each other and also directly identifies the top and bottom boundaries to each other.
Topology2D.Torus() - Constructor for class topology.Topology2D.Torus
